br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb03b693db34d22c076f131e639a3043465942f","tid":1230311,"uid":37220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:18:06.000Z","msg":"1514 市民如打算於尖沙咀乘坐天星小輪前往港島，請留意目前龍尾排到星光大道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請儘快轉移其他碼頭"},{"pid":"5a45b5b552e4598063ecfed99c747c10ddbc30b2","tid":1230311,"uid":126283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"觀塘碼頭1個鐘一班<br />\n逢XX：30開船"},{"pid":"fc26c23331924cc08da8d5942b68c0acb75eaa9e","tid":1230311,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a45b5b552e4598063ecfed99c747c10ddbc30b2","tid":1230311,"uid":126283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"觀塘碼頭1個鐘一班<br />\n逢XX：30開船"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒<br />\n唔記得左觀塘都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2340662053b23d65f6e42700a4aca97b6ee4a9","tid":1230311,"uid":37220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅磡去北角<br />\n<br />\n每個小時 05 / 35 分鐘有船</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"cbe55d0d4a78c4c729b8a3a02424570def48223e","tid":1230311,"uid":76403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f2340662053b23d65f6e42700a4aca97b6ee4a9","tid":1230311,"uid":37220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅磡去北角<br />\n<br />\n每個小時 05 / 35 分鐘有船</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"紅磡九龍城都係<br />\n九龍城應該未夠人坐滿一班船"},{"pid":"0943790307f72bad7c2c1a6